## Proficiencies

Skills begin at 1 point and starting characters can allocate 2 extra points in any one of the skill, or 1 point on each different.

### Skills
Boating
Crafting
Fishing
Foraging
Hunting
Medicine
Mining
Speechcraft
Stealth
Storytelling
Survival
Tracking
Trapping

### Lores
Terrain
Weather
Herbs
Predators
Hostiles
Castilians
